            "text": "<p>Preet Bhullar is a microbiologist. She spent years studying what goes into food at a molecular level — and what she found in most \"health\" products didn't sit right. Fillers disguised as ingredients. Additives with names longer than the nutrition panel. Marketing that said \"natural\" while the contents said otherwise.</p><p>So she stopped buying what the market offered and went looking for the real thing. Direct to the farms. Direct to the source. That search became Divine Ingredients.</p>"
